      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a second that he isn't there, but then it hits me all over again. the house feels like a tomb. i dont even know why i bother getting out of bed anymore. what is even the point of waking up to a world that doesn't have him in it? it just feels hollow.",
